4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp, designed to transform beginners into skilled developers in just 18 weeks. The program focuses on essential technologies like JavaScript and Python, enabling participants to build websites and apps, consume data via APIs, and develop their own projects for hands-on experience.

Classes are conducted three times a week, maintaining a low student-to-teacher ratio of 7:1. No prior coding experience is necessary, and courses are available in both English and Spanish. Upon completion, students receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate.

